OL,3,CPubs in Jersey can stay open until 4am
OL,4,Cfor England World Cup match
OL,6,FPubs will remain open until 4am on
OL,7,FMonday morning in Jersey after the
OL,8,FGovernment announced an extension of
OL,9,Fhours to let fans watch England's tie
OL,10,Fagainst Mexico.
OL,12,FThe move comes after UK Prime Minister
OL,13,FSir Keir Starmer stepped in to reverse
OL,14,Fplans there and allow venues in
OL,15,FEngland and Wales to open until 5am.
OL,17,FIt had been reported that the island
OL,18,Fwas unlikely to further change closing
OL,19,Ftimes.
