OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1783698492
OL,3,CPubs in Jersey can stay open until 4am
OL,4,Cfor England World Cup match
OL,6,FAt the end of May, Jersey's government
OL,7,Fannounced that establishments could
OL,8,Fapply for a special licence to open
OL,9,Funtil 2am on a game by game basis.
OL,11,FThat meant Scotland fans were unable
OL,12,Fto watch their first group game
OL,13,Fagainst Haiti, which started at the
OL,14,Fsame time places had to close.
OL,16,FSimilarly, Portugal supporters were
OL,17,Fonly able to watch some of their match
OL,18,Fagainst Colombia, which kicked off at
OL,19,F12:30am.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
