PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1783698492
OL,3,CPubs in Jersey can stay open until 4am
OL,4,Cfor England World Cup match
OL,6,FAs with other World Cup licence
OL,7,Fextensions, venues with over 60
OL,8,Fcustomers will have to hire security.
OL,10,FThey will also be expected to enforce
OL,11,Flast orders at 3:30am.
OL,13,FStates of Jersey Police told ITV News
OL,14,Fthey will "review" resourcing
OL,15,Farrangements that "have operational
OL,16,Fimplications".
OL,18,FThey "support" the decision to extend
OL,19,Fhours, but encouraged pub-goers to
OL,20,F"enjoy the occasion responsibly".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
