PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1783698492
OL,3,CPubs in Jersey can stay open until 4am
OL,4,Cfor England World Cup match
OL,6,FIf England progress further through
OL,7,Fthe tournament, their games will
OL,8,Fconclude before the previously
OL,9,Fannounced 2am cut-off.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, Guernsey is expected to
OL,12,Fstick to its current arrangement,
OL,13,Fwhich allows venues to open until 2am.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/4
